://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DeChambeausecured his second majorat Pinehurst last weekend, edging outRory McIlroy in North Carolina.\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 688, \"end\": 702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Carolina\", \"score\": 0.9415584525583985, \"rank\": 0.054920758222881005, \"text\": \"North Carolina\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Carolina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Carolina\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It continued an excellent year in golf's biggest events for the LIV Golf star, with a tie for sixth at The Masters followed by arunner-up finish at the PGA Championship.\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 769, \"end\": 777, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LIV Golf\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That strong major form has not been enough, though, for the 30-year-old to force his way into a four-player American squad drawn from the PGA Tour, with DeChambeau only rising to 10th in the Official World Golf Rankings that determine selection.\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 984, \"end\": 992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999979595486, \"rank\": 1.1561954260935547e-09, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1014, \"end\": 1022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/PGA_Tour\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9023182935668424e-50, \"text\": \"PGA Tour\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/PGA_Tour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/r